c: 12
v: 37
t: "Yosefe adati, “Palibe chakudya chimene mumalandira, ngati chakudya chanu, chimene chidze kwa inu ine ndisanamasulire tanthauzo lake. Ichi ndicho chimene Ambuye wanga adandiphunzitsa. Ndithudi ine ndasiya chipembedzo cha anthu osakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndiponso m’moyo umene uli nkudza.”"